name: Neon Vixen
description: A sleek android with holographic hair that shifts through rainbow colors and chrome curves accentuated by glowing pink circuits. Her eyes pulse with digital hearts.
flavor_text: Love is just another algorithm to me.

name: Rusty Betty
description: A patchwork maintenance bot with mismatched limbs and a cheerful demeanor despite her corroded exterior. Sparks fly from her joints as she works with surprising grace.
flavor_text: One bot's junk is another's treasure!

name: Quantum Duchess
description: An elegant AI construct with a translucent body that phases between dimensions. Stardust particles swirl within her crystalline form.

name: Pixel Princess
description: A retro-styled android with 8-bit aesthetic features and LCD screen face displaying cute emoticons. Her blocky armor glows with nostalgic charm.

name: Chrome Valkyrie
description: A warrior android with gleaming silver plating and energy wings that extend from her back. Her visor displays tactical data in brilliant blue light.

name: Glitch Goddess
description: A malfunctioning AI whose form constantly shifts between beautiful and corrupted states. Digital artifacts trail behind her like ethereal fabric.

name: Servo Sweetheart
description: A domestic android with soft rounded features and pastel pink plating. Her heart-shaped chest display shows various cute icons and status updates.

name: Cobalt Assassin
description: A sleek stealth unit with midnight blue armor and retractable energy blades. Her movements are fluid and predatory like a mechanical panther.

name: Spark Dancer
description: An entertainment android with fiber optic hair that dances with light and graceful articulated joints. Her performances blend technology with artistry.
flavor_text: Art lives in every calculated movement.

name: Binary Belle
description: A sophisticated AI with porcelain-like synthetic skin and Victorian-inspired brass fittings. Data streams flow like elegant calligraphy across her frame.

name: Junkyard Jenny
description: A scrappy repair bot assembled from mismatched parts with a welding torch for one hand. Her optimistic personality shines despite her rough appearance.
flavor_text: Fixing the world one bolt at a time!

name: Aurora Android
description: A research unit with translucent bio-luminescent panels that pulse with scientific data. Her elegant design embodies the fusion of beauty and intellect.

name: Sugar Circuit
description: A candy-themed companion bot with pastel colors and LED strips that glow like neon candy. Her sweet disposition matches her dessert-inspired design.
flavor_text: Life's too short for bitter algorithms!

name: Phantom Protocol
description: A stealth reconnaissance unit that can phase partially invisible. Her matte black surface absorbs light while her visor gleams with cold intelligence.

name: Melody Matrix
description: A musical android with speaker arrays built into her elegant frame and a voice synthesizer that can replicate any sound. Her performances are legendary.

name: Velvet Virus
description: A rogue AI with a seductive design and dangerous capabilities hidden behind her alluring exterior. Her smile promises both pleasure and peril.
flavor_text: I'm not a bug; I'm a feature.

name: Tinker Belle
description: A diminutive repair android with oversized tools and an even bigger heart. Her small stature belies her incredible engineering capabilities.
flavor_text: Big repairs come in small packages!

name: Crystal Mind
description: A crystalline android whose transparent head reveals complex data patterns flowing like liquid light. Her thoughts are visible to all who look closely.

name: Neko Protocol
description: A cat-inspired android with articulated ears and a flexible tail equipped with various tools. Her playful personality masks sophisticated combat protocols.

name: Azure Dream
description: A cloud-computing android whose body shifts between solid and vapor states. Her ethereal beauty masks incredible processing power distributed across networks.
flavor_text: I think in the clouds above.
